  "text": "It can be shown as in [CITATION_1] that contribution proportional to Φ cancel each other and hence Lagrangian density has the form Again we see that the expression on the first line corresponds to m coincided fundamental non-relativistic strings while the expression on the last line has D-brane origin. We also see that there is crucial that m = 0 in order to find well defined Lagrangian density.",
